snippet.title: Prison Boss Prohibition | Upload VR Showcase 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
New Alpha Access starts December 11th, 2024. Join us now on Discord: http://discord.gg/prisonboss

Prison Boss Prohibition is a humorous VR crafting and trading game where you run various shops across New Yolk City. Produce and sell merchandise that's both strictly legal and… questionably not—all to get ridiculously rich!

Website: https://prisonboss.fun 
X: https://x.com/Prison_Boss_ 
TikTok: @‌trebuchetstudio 
Wishlist on Meta Quest: https://bit.ly/PBP_MetaQuest 
Wishlist on Steam: https://bit.ly/PBP_Steam
